snippet.title: Live Class 10th English Full Revision Of Grammar | CBSE Class 10th Grammar One Shot | Watch Now
snippet.description:
Welcome to our YouTube live video on "10th English Full Revision of Grammar." In this video, we'll cover all the essential topics of CBSE Class 10th Grammar in one shot.

Whether you're preparing for your board exams or want to brush up on your grammar skills, this live class is the perfect opportunity for you to learn everything you need to know about English grammar.

Our expert instructor will also share some tips and tricks to help you remember grammar rules and avoid common mistakes. We'll provide you with plenty of practice exercises and answer any questions you may have about grammar.

ప్రేమించిన యువతి కోసం తోటి స్నేహితుడినే హత్య చేశాడు ఓ కిరాతక మిత్రుడు.  గొంతు నులిమి చంపి.. కర్కశంగా తలను మొండెం నుంచి వేరు చేశాడు. ప్రేయసిని బెదిరించాడని గుండే చీల్చాడు. చేతి వేళ్లను నరికాడు. హత్య చేసిన 2 రోజుల తర్వాత మృతుడి తండ్రికి ఫోన్ చేసి ఏమీ తెలియనట్లు మాట్లాడాడు నిందితుడు. సైకోలా మారి హత్యకు పాల్పడిన తీరును చూసి.. పోలీసులే నివ్వెరపోయారు. హైదరాబాద్‌ శివారులోని అబ్దుల్లాపూర్ మెట్ పోలీస్‌స్టేషన్‌ పరిధిలోని నిర్మానుష ప్రాంతంలో ఈ హత్య చోటు చేసుకుంది.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3703 - 24 Feb 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3703: Bhide Ka Sar Dard
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide was overjoyed to learn of Tapu's girlfriend, and he made "sheera" to inform Madhavi of the news. By telling him the truth that Missa is only a friend and there was a misunderstanding, Sonu breaks his bubble. When Tapu arrives at the society's compound, he decides to play cricket with Tapu Sena in order to remember the memories of his youth. Jetha, Babita, and Dr. Hathi become the audience of the cricket match, Tapu plays a scoop shot on Goli's ball, causing it to strike Bhide on his balcony. Stay tuned!

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3702 - 23 Feb 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3702: Gada Pariwaar Ki Nayi Bahu
--------------------------------------------------------
Missa, a friend of Tapu shows up at the Gokuldham society to meet Tapu and give him his diary. Champaklal and Jetha enjoy seeing Tapu interacting warmly with his friend, and Bapuji thinks Missa could end up being their daughter-in-law. Jetha is taken aback by Champaklal's statements, while Sonu exhibits a depressed mood. Missa is brought over by Tapu, who also introduces her to his family. Bapuji is overjoyed to see her because he considers her to be cultured and well-educated. Tapu prevents Sonu from leaving the house while Misha compliments Tapu's coffee and denies having tea made by Sonu. Bhide arrives at his balcony, where he is thrilled to see Missa with Tapu. Stay tuned!

Our Dear Sir will guide you through the important topics and concepts that you need to focus on and provide you with valuable insights on how to present your paper in a way that will impress your examiner.

Whether you are struggling with grammar or literature or Passages, this class will provide you with the necessary tools and techniques to tackle these challenges effectively.

So, join us for this informative and interactive session and take the first step towards acing your Class 10th English exam!

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3701 - Sonu Layi Tapu Ke Liye Nashta?! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada

snippet.title: Live Class 10th English Full Revision Of All Poems | First Flight English Textbook All Poem Revision
snippet.description:
Welcome to the Dear Sir channel's YouTube Live session on "Full Revision of All Poems from Class 10th English Textbook - First Flight". This live session is designed to help students revise all the poems in their English textbook thoroughly.

During this live session, we will cover all the poems included in the Class 10th English textbook, First Flight. The session will provide a comprehensive revision of all the poems, ensuring that students have a clear understanding of the themes, literary devices, and overall structure of each poem.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3704 - 25 Feb 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3704: Tapu Aur Champaklal Ka Dance
--------------------------------------------------------
When Bagha and Nattu Kaka confront Jethalal for being late, Jethalal responds humorously that he couldn't understand the language. Bagha informs Jetha that four items from the shop have already been sold, making Jetha delighted. Jetha informs them that Tapu has returned from Andhra Pradesh and that he spent the morning enjoying time with his adored son. Bawri enters the store and informs them that she has to buy a 10 lakh rupee television. Everyone is astonished by this because previously she would visit the shop to meet Bagha, but this time was different. Remain tuned!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3704, 25 Feb 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000211115

snippet.title: Tere Bin Ep 18 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 18 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 23rd February 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

எங்களின் அபிமான SK Sir தனது புதிய குழும  மாணவர்களுடன் பொறுமை, விடாமுயற்சி மற்றும் அர்ப்பணிப்பு ஆகியவற்றின் புதிய பரிமாணத்தில் மீண்டும் வருகிறார். 

Meta is helping build a future where people have more ways to play and connect in the metaverse. The metaverse may be virtual, but the impact will be real. Learn more at https://about.meta.com/metaverse/impact/

Ashish Arora, SK Sir அவர்களின் புதிய மாணவர்  - வாழ்க்கையில் ஒன்றிலிருந்து அடுத்த விஷயத்திற்குத் தாவுவதை வழக்கமாகக் கொண்டுள்ளார், மேலும் எல்லாவற்றையும் முழுமையடையாமல் விட்டுவிடுகிறார். SK Sir தனது புதிய மாணவனை எப்படி எதிர்கொள்வார்?

Episode 02 Releasing On 27th February 2023
Audio Available in Hindi, Tamil or Telugu

Credits:
Directed by: Pratish Mehta
Written by: Prashant Kumar
Executive Producers: Vijay Koshy, Deepak Kumar Mishra, Anandeshwar Dwivedi

Background Score: Rohan Rohan

Cast: Abhilash Thapliyal, Gagan Arora, Naveen Kasturia, Shivankit Singh Parihar, Badri Chavan, Rajesh Jais, Venus Singh

#brawltalk  #mysteryatthehub #masteries 

An epic battle royale made for mobile! Play with friends or solo across a variety of game modes in under three minutes.

Unlock and upgrade dozens of Brawlers with powerful Super abilities, Star Powers and Gadgets! Collect unique skins to stand out and show off. Battle in a variety of mysterious locations within the Brawliverse!

BATTLE IN MULTIPLE GAME MODES
- Gem Grab (3v3): Team up and out-strategize the opposing team. Collect and hold 10 gems to win, but get fragged and lose your gems.
- Showdown (Solo/Duo): A battle royale style fight for survival. Collect power ups for your Brawler. Grab a friend or play solo - be the last Brawler standing in the rowdiest battle royale yet. Winner take all!
- Brawl Ball (3v3): It's a whole new Brawl game! Show off your soccer/football skills and score two goals before the other team. There are no red cards here.
- Bounty (3v3): Take out opponents to earn stars, but don’t let them pick you off. The squad with the most stars wins the match!
- Heist (3v3): Protect your team’s safe and try to crack open your opponents’. Navigate the map to sneak, blast and blow your way clear to the enemies treasure.
- Special Events: Limited time special PvE and PvP game modes.
- Championship Challenge: Join Brawl Stars' esports scene with in-game qualifiers!

UNLOCK AND UPGRADE BRAWLERS
Collect and upgrade a variety of Brawlers with powerful Super abilities, Star Powers and Gadgets! Level them up and collect unique skins.

BRAWL PASS
Complete quests, open Brawl Boxes, earn Gems, pins and an exclusive Brawl Pass skin! Fresh content every season.

BECOME THE STAR PLAYER
Climb the local and regional leaderboards to prove you’re the greatest Brawler of them all!

CONSTANTLY EVOLVING
Look out for new Brawlers, skins, maps, special events and games modes in the future.

PLEASE NOTE! Brawl Stars is free to download and play, however, some game items can also be purchased for real money. If you don't want to use this feature, please disable in-app purchases in your device's settings. Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 9 years of age to play or download Brawl Stars.

Features:
- Team up for real-time 3v3 battles against players from across the world
- A fast-paced multiplayer battle royale mode made for mobile
- Unlock and collect new, powerful Brawlers - each with a signature attack and Super ability
- New events and game modes daily
- Battle solo or with friends
- Climb to the top of the leaderboards in global and local rankings 
- Join or start your own Club with fellow players to share tips and battle together
- Customize Brawlers with unlockable skins
- Player-designed maps offer challenging new terrain to master

From the makers of Clash of Clans, Clash Royale and Boom Beach!

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel.

In this video, I share with you 7 Wrong Food combinations that you are eating daily and how you can easily avoid them.

02:04 - #6 Tomato and Cucumber -  If you often consume tomato and cucumber together then Ayurveda advises that you better stop doing so.

snippet.title: $3 Trillion Lithium Found in J&K | Geopolitics of Natural Resources | Dhruv Rathee
snippet.description:
Recently, the ministry of mines announced that ∼ 60 lakh metric tonnes of lithium, or "white gold," or "new oil," had been found in Jammu and Kashmir. Although lithium has been discovered in India before, this is the first time such large quantities have been discovered. But what does this lithium mean for India's growth? Who will extract it? Is all of it actually mineable? When can we expect the results of the assessment? How can we exploit these reserves to their fullest potential? Watch this video by Dhruv Rathee to find out!

en.description:
Recently, the ministry of mines announced that ∼ 60 lakh metric tonnes of lithium, or "white gold," or "new oil," had been found in Jammu and Kashmir. Although lithium has been discovered in India before, this is the first time such large quantities have been discovered. But what does this lithium mean for India's growth? Who will extract it? snippet.title: Tere Bin Episode 19 Teaser - 23rd February 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 19 Teaser - 23rd February 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment
